t%20the%20best%20rate%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20Does%20the%20Fed%20Affect%20Mortgage%20Rates%3F%5C%22%3EHow%20Does%20the%20Fed%20Affect%20Mortgage%20Rates%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20aggressively%20raised%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-the-federal-funds-rate%5C%22%3Efederal%20funds%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%20and%202023%20to%20slow%20economic%20growth%20and%20get%20inflation%20under%20control.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20spiked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20aren't%20directly%20impacted%20by%20changes%20to%20the%20federal%20funds%20rate%2C%20but%20they%20often%20trend%20up%20or%20down%20ahead%20of%20Fed%20policy%20moves.%20This%20is%20because%20mortgage%20rates%20change%20based%20on%20investor%20demand%20for%20mortgage-backed%20securities%2C%20and%20this%20demand%20is%20often%20impacted%20by%20how%20investors%20expect%20Fed%20hikes%20to%20affect%20the%20broader%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20it's%20looking%20like%20the%20Fed%20will%20cut%20rates%20soon%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20have%20dropped.%20And%20they%20could%20decrease%20more%20depending%20on%20how%20quickly%20the%20Fed%20lowers%20its%20benchmark%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Mortgage%20Rate%20Predictions%202025%5C%22%3EMortgage%20Rate%20Predictions%202025%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20have%20been%20going%20down%20in%20recent%20months.%20But%20it's%20unclear%20how%20much%20further%20they'll%20drop%20or%20where%20they%20could%20ultimately%20end%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20are%20expected%20to%20continue%20trending%20down%20in%202025%20as%20the%20Fed%20lowers%20its%20benchmark%20rate%20and%20inflation%20cools.%20But%20that%20forecast%20could%20change%20depending%20on%20how%20the%20economy%20evolves%20next%20year.%20Right%20now%2C%20the%20Fed%20is%20poised%20to%20achieve%20a%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bsoft%20landing%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20it%20successfully%20brings%20inflation%20back%20down%20to%20its%202%25%20target%20without%20sparking%20an%20economic%20downturn.%20In%20this%20scenario%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20may%20only%20decrease%20moderately%20in%202025.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20economy%20cools%20too%20much%20and%20a%20recession%20looks%20likely%2C%20rates%20may%20fall%20more%20substantially.%20Or%2C%20if%20inflation%20stops%20decelerating%20or%20ticks%20back%20up%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20could%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-monday-16-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726480803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F626bff7886fa90001905cc40%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-monday-16-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20are%20today's%20mortgage%20and%20refinance%20rates.%20Mortgage%20rates%20are%20down%20ahead%20of%20this%20week's%20Fed%20meeting%2C%20and%20they%20should%20fall%20further%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Molly%20Grace)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-monday-16-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%2027-year-old%20who%20quit%20her%20job%20to%20resell%20sneakers%20online%20explains%20how%20she%20got%20her%20start%20and%20sourced%20profitable%20products%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22val%20zapata%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e48c1dcfb7f307e57185f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVal%20Zapata%2C%20founder%20of%20The%20Shoe%20Game%20Co.%2C%20has%20a%20team%20of%20eight%20employees%20and%20a%206%2C000-square-foot%20warehouse.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Val%20Zapata%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVal%20Zapata%20has%20sold%20millions%20in%20sneakers%20and%20streetwear%20via%20live%20shows%20on%20Whatnot.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHer%20business%2C%20The%20Shoe%20Game%20Co.%2C%20evolved%20from%20a%20hobby%20to%20a%20full-time%20venture%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EZapata%20sources%20deals%20online%2C%20builds%20networks%2C%20and%20educates%20buyers%20to%20maximize%20sales.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20Val%20Zapata%20has%20sold%20millions%20of%20dollars%20worth%20of%20sneakers%20and%20streetwear%20by%20hosting%20live%20shows%20on%20the%20marketplace%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatnot.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhatnot%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Business%20Insider%20verified%20her%20sales%20by%20looking%20at%20her%20company's%20Whatnot%20seller%20dashboard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHer%20business%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftheshoe.gameco%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Shoe%20Game%20Co.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20started%20as%20a%20hobby%20before%20evolving%20into%20a%20side%20hustle%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20a%20full-time%20gig.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe's%20been%20flipping%20shoes%20with%20her%20dad%20since%20she%20was%20a%20teen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20come%20from%20a%20wealthy%20home.%20The%20reality%20was%2C%20my%20dad%20just%20did%20what%20he%20could%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zapata%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20Colombia%20and%20grew%20up%20in%20New%20York%20and%20Texas.%20%26quot%3BBut%20when%20we%20wanted%20something%2C%20he%20would%20do%20anything%20to%20figure%20it%20out.%20He%20would%20be%20like%2C%20'OK%2C%20you%20want%20one%20of%20these%20sneakers%3F%20Let's%20buy%20five%20of%20them%2C%20sell%20them%2C%20collect%20that%20%2430%20or%20%2440%20or%20%2450%20profit%2C%20and%20then%20we'll%20buy%20you%20your%20pair.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20she%20grew%20older%2C%20she%20directed%20less%20time%20toward%20her%20sneaker%20hobby%20and%20more%20toward%20her%20career.%20She%20skipped%20college%20and%20started%20working%20as%20a%20life%20insurance%20broker.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESneakers%20didn't%20reappear%20on%20her%20radar%20until%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20when%20work%20became%20stressful%20and%20her%20girlfriend%20encouraged%20her%20to%20reconnect%20with%20her%20childhood%20hobby%20as%20a%20way%20to%20decompress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d117f389-ef34-4ea7-8490-3ef6160b3412%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETurning%20a%20hobby%20into%20a%20side%20hustle%20by%20finding%20deals%20online%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EZapata%20didn't%20build%20a%20seven-figure%20business%20overnight.%20She%20started%20by%20browsing%20sites%20like%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20and%20OfferUp%20for%20deals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20likens%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20to%20%26quot%3Ban%20online%20garage%20sale%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20says%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3EOfferUp%20is%20%26quot%3Blike%20the%20magic%20cheat%20code.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20typical%20seller%20on%20these%20types%20of%20platforms%20is%20a%20regular%20person%20looking%20to%20make%20some%20extra%20cash%20on%20an%20item%20that's%20been%20sitting%20around%20the%20house%20for%20years%2C%20she%20explained.%20That%20means%20they're%20willing%20to%20negotiate%2C%20and%20there's%20an%20opportunity%20for%20collectors%20and%20resellers%20who%20truly%20know%20their%20niche%20to%20score%20deals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20industry%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20would%20find%20these%20really%2C%20really%20high-end%20sneakers%20%E2%80%94%20like%2C%20%241%2C000%20sneakers%20%E2%80%94%20on%20there%20for%20%24150%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20noting%20that%2C%20with%20shoes%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20verify%20something%20is%20what%20the%20seller%20says%20it%20is.%20Zapata%20learned%20this%20lesson%20the%20hard%20way%20by%20purchasing%2050%20pairs%20of%20fake%20Yeezys%20and%20swallowing%20about%20%242%2C500.%20It%20was%20early%20in%20her%20reselling%20career%20and%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3Eso%20much%20money%20at%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22val%20zapata%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e47ca1d17aa3c7b2b28b2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZapata's%20warehouse%20is%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20where%20she%20moved%20in%202024.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Val%20Zapata%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20gradually%20built%20a%20network%20of%20trusted%20buyers%20and%20sellers%20in%20the%20industry.%20Whenever%20she%20met%20another%20reseller%2C%20she%20would%20ask%20for%20their%20Instagram%20handle.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20I%20would%20watch%20his%20story%20and%20figure%20out%20who%20he%20was%20doing%20business%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zapata.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20built%20a%20little%20tiny%20network%20through%20all%20my%20local%20resellers%2C%20and%20that%20grew%20to%20me%20learning%20about%20trade%20shows.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20early%20piece%20of%20advice%20she%20heard%20from%20another%20reseller%20stuck%20with%20her%3A%20%26quot%3BConnections%20over%20profits.%20Grow%20your%20connections%20so%20people%20will%20always%20sell%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20never%20know%20who%20you'll%20meet%20if%20you%20put%20yourself%20out%20there%20on%20social%20media%20and%20attend%20events%20and%20trade%20shows.%20Zapata%20says%20the%20best%20deals%20she%20scored%20came%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Brandom%26quot%3B%20event%20in%20Boston%20in%20early%202024.%20It%20was%20a%20relatively%20mellow%20scene%2C%20except%20for%20one%20seller%20with%20a%20megaphone.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20the%20only%20person%20who's%20excited%2C%20and%20he's%20like%2C%20'I've%20got%20shoes%20for%20sale.%20Everything's%20got%20to%20go.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20shoes%20had%20price%20tags%2C%20but%20Zapata%20decided%20to%20try%20her%20hand%20at%20negotiating.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20like%2C%20'Listen%2C%20I'm%20just%20going%20to%20shoot%20you%20some%20offers%2C'%26quot%3B%20recalled%20Zapata%2C%20who%20picked%20up%20a%20shoe%20with%20a%20%24600%20tag%20on%20it%20and%20offered%20%24150.%20The%20seller%20countered%20with%20%24160.%20She%20took%20the%20deal%20and%20moved%20on%20to%20a%20second%20sneaker%2C%20which%20she%20negotiated%20down%20to%20%2480.%20%26quot%3BHe%20either%20had%20no%20context%2C%20or%20he%20just%20didn't%20care.%20I%20look%20at%20my%20team%20and%20I'm%20like%2C%20'Grab%20everything%20we%20could%20possibly%20take%2C%20put%20it%20against%20the%20wall%2C%20and%20then%20we%20will%20negotiate%2C'%20because%20I%20could%20see%20that%20people%20were%20starting%20to%20realize%20what%20was%20happening.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20walked%20away%20with%20about%20450%20pairs%20of%20shoes%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20we%20nearly%20quadrupled%20our%20money%20on%20that%20deal%2C%20which%20never%20happens%20in%20sneakers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20a%20once-in-a-blue-moon%20deal%20that%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20possible%20if%20Zapata%20didn't%20know%20her%20niche%20as%20well%20as%20she%20does.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20market%20changes%20constantly.%20She%20stays%20up-to-date%20on%20what's%20popular%20by%20attending%20events%2C%20paying%20attention%20to%20what%20people%20are%20wearing%2C%20and%20observing%20what%20her%20favorite%20sellers%20are%20buying%20and%20avoiding.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe%20try%20to%20find%20a%20medium%20where%20we%20find%20what's%20popular%20right%20now%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20Yeezy%20GAP%20is%20popular%20right%20now%2C%20AntiSocialSocialClub%20and%20Supreme%20will%20always%20be%20popular%20in%20the%20streetwear%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20we%20try%20to%20find%20more%20everyday%20brands%20that%20people%20also%20love%2C%20like%20your%20Nikes%20and%20Adidas.%20The%20things%20that%20are%20always%20tried%20and%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zapata%2C%20whose%20company%20has%20expanded%20into%20streetwear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20a%20while%2C%20however%2C%20she%20says%20she%20stuck%20to%20what%20she%20knew%20best%2C%20which%20were%20retro%20Jordan%20sneakers%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20veer%20off.%20I%20didn't%20sell%20the%20Nike%20SB%20until%20maybe%20six%20months%20ago%20because%20I%20didn't%20understand%20what%20a%20Nike%20SB%20really%20was.%20So%20we%20stayed%20within%20our%20frame%20of%20what%20we%20knew%20and%20what%20our%20customer%20liked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESourcing%20the%20product%20is%20half%20the%20battle.%20She%20then%20has%20to%20sell%2C%20which%20she%20predominantly%20does%20through%20live%20shows%20on%20Whatnot.%20She's%20found%20that%20the%20more%20she%20can%20educate%20her%20buyers%2C%20the%20more%20successful%20she%20is.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BHolly%20might%20come%20on%20and%20say%2C%20'I%20love%20that%20pink%20sneaker%2C'%20and%20bid.%20But%20if%20I%20tell%20Holly%2C%20not%20only%20is%20this%20a%20really%20cool%20pink%20sneaker%2C%20but%20this%20is%20a%202020%20collectible%20from%20Kobe%20Bryant%2C%20Holly%20might%20be%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20little%20bit%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Zapata%2C%20who%20starts%20every%20product%20at%20a%20dollar%20during%20a%20live%20show.%20The%20highest%20bidder%20takes%20it%20home.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20I%20don't%20know%20and%20don't%20share%2C%20then%20they're%20just%20consumers%20bidding%20and%20trying%20to%20get%20a%20good%20deal.%20So%20I%20learned%20very%20early%20on%20that%20I%20have%20to%20bring%20knowledge%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fan-entrepreneur-who-resells-sneakers-explains-how-she-sources-products-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726480803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e48e8fd17aa3c7b2b293b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fan-entrepreneur-who-resells-sneakers-explains-how-she-sources-products-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sneaker%20reseller%20Val%20Zapata%20started%20sourcing%20products%20on%20sites%20like%20OfferUp%2C%20which%20she%20describes%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20magic%20cheat%20code.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fan-entrepreneur-who-resells-sneakers-explains-how-she-sources-products-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22London%20Film%20Festival%3A%20Working%20Title%20Heads%2C%20Apple%20TV%2B%20Euro%20Boss%2C%20%E2%80%98Zone%20of%20Interest%E2%80%99%20Sound%20Designer%20Among%20Industry%20Lineup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726480800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTim-Bevan-and-Eric-Fellner.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236145680%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%202024%20BFI%20London%20Film%20Festival%20has%20unveiled%20a%20bustling%20lineup%20of%20speakers%20and%20events%20for%20its%20industry%20forum.%20Set%20to%20take%20place%20between%20Oct.%2010-16%20at%20the%20Picturehouse%20Central%20cinema%20in%20cen