0particularly%20Gen%20Zers%2C%20whose%20brains%20were%20still%20developing%2C%20Neo%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnresolved%20trauma%20and%20mental%20health%20challenges%20put%20us%20in%20a%20state%20of%20fight%2C%20flight%2C%20freeze%2C%20or%20fawn%2C%20with%20our%20amygdala%20%E2%80%94%20the%20fear%20center%20of%20the%20brain%20%E2%80%94%20firing%20up%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20can%20make%20us%20more%20impulsive%2C%20less%20thoughtful%20of%20our%20choices%2C%20and%20can%20be%20a%20risk%20factor%20for%20romance%20scams%2C%26quot%3B%20Neo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeo%20said%20scammers%20are%20highly%20sophisticated%20at%20creating%20profiles%20they%20think%20their%20marks%20will%20like.%20For%20some%2C%20this%20may%20involve%20a%20life%20of%20luxury%2C%20which%20may%20include%20travel%2C%20fancy%20meals%2C%20and%20expensive%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20also%20well-versed%20in%20manipulation%2C%20she%20added%2C%20knowing%20that%20with%20the%20right%20push%20and%20pull%20of%20attention%2C%20they%20can%20hook%20their%20victims%20in%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-love-bombing-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove-bombing%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20playing%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fanxious-attachment-style%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efears%20of%20abandonment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20trained%20to%20answer%20them%2C%20and%20you're%20trained%20to%20give%20them%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20Neo%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20trained%20to%20trust%20them%2C%20and%20then%20they%20start%20to%20build%20this%20idea%20of%20the%20future%20together%20really%2C%20really%20fast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a06a6c0a-ba0d-49c2-9fc8-f39c568393ca%5C%22%3EA%20shared%20struggle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20bond%20is%20formed%2C%20scammers%20will%20get%20to%20work.%20Gen%20Zers%20understand%20what%2