E2%80%94%20to%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20appointments%2C%20and%20dates%20%E2%80%94%20so%20I%20sold%20my%20car.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20self-conscious%20initially%2C%20but%20run-commuting%20helped%20me%20build%20strength%2C%20confidence%2C%20and%20community.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20a%20sunny%20summer%20evening%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-do-in-seattle-washington%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20Seattle%2C%20Washington%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20I%20am%20running%20down%20a%20sidewalk%20in%20chic%20sandals%20and%20a%20floral%20dress%2C%20phone%20in%20hand%20and%20ponytail%20trailing%20in%20the%20wind.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20one%20is%20chasing%20me.%20Rather%2C%20I've%20just%20gotten%20out%20of%20church%20and%20would%20like%20to%20get%20takeout%20before%20this%20restaurant%20closes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESure%2C%20I%20could%20walk%2C%20catch%20a%20bus%2C%20or%20summon%20a%20rideshare%20(and%20I%20often%20do)%20%E2%80%94%20but%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flearn-to-love-running-after-hating-it-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20prefer%20to%20run%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It's%20at%20least%2050%25%20faster%20than%20walking%20and%20avoids%20the%20carbon%20emissions%20of%20using%20a%20vehicle.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20I've%20logged%20270%20miles%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-run-to-work-every-day-whats-in-my-backpack-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erun-commutes%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%2011%25%20of%20my%20total%20running%20mileage.%20But%20I%20haven't%20always%20been%20a%20runner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22483a3831-bf89-46b0-af2b-eee2c50a9ebf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20run-commuting%20began%20out%20of%20necessity%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20wasn't%20my%20plan.%20In%20April%202021%2C%20I%20proudly%20took%20home%20a%20shiny%2C%20dark%20blue%20Prius%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoyota-prius-is-most-important-car-last-20-years-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20first%20car%20I%20bought%20myself%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20When%20I%20moved%20to%20Seattle%20in%20January%202022%2C%20I%20intended%20to%20ship%20my%20car%20from%20Florida%20once%20I%20got%20settled%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-in-walkable-neighborhood-could-help-you-live-100-study-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20walked%20most%20places%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20But%20one%20day%2C%20I%20was%20late%20for%20an%20appointment%20that%20was%20two%20miles%20away%20%E2%80%94%20too%20far%20to%20walk%20there%20in%20time%2C%20but%20too%20close%20to%20justify%20ordering%20a%20Lyft.%20So%2C%20I%20started%20running.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20hooked.%20From%20there%2C%20I%20often%20ran%20anywhere%20within%20a%20three-mile%20radius%3A%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20the%20hair%20salon%2C%20dinner%20dates%2C%20and%20church.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221dc593b5-3f4f-49ec-bbab-387f7b0b4121%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EInitially%2C%20I%20felt%20out%20of%20place%2C%20uncomfortable%20with%20being%20seen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20felt%20self-conscious.%20I%20even%20bought%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wearing-backpack-rucking-working-out-build-muscle-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especial%20running%20backpack%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20had%20a%20vest%20and%20hydration%20pack%2C%20thinking%20this%20would%20help%20me%20look%20the%20part.%20That's%20because%20not%20many%20run-commuters%20look%20like%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20statistics%20on%20it%20are%20scarce%2C%20in%202014%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheruncommuter.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F11%2F2014-ISORC-Results.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Run%20Commuter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20surveyed%20145%20run-commuters%20in%2022%20countries%20and%20found%20that%20only%20about%2030%25%20were%20women.%20And%202021%20research%20published%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0966692321000910%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJournal%20of%20Transport%20Geography%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3Econcluded%20that%20run-commuting%20is%20%26quot%3Bmost%20popular%20with%20urban-dwelling%20middle-aged%20white%20men%20in%20highly%20paid%20professional%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20an%20Asian%20American%20woman%20in%20my%2030s%20who%20makes%20a%20living%20writing%2C%20I%20am%20not%20your%20typical%20run-commuter.%20And%20for%20someone%20who%20has%20always%20longed%20to%20fit%20in%2C%20this%20was%20not%20welcome%20news.%20There%20was%20a%20period%20of%20my%20life%20where%20I%20would%20run%20only%20at%20night%20just%20to%20avoid%20being%20seen.%20Now%2C%20I%20couldn't%20help%20but%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEventually%2C%20I%20stopped%20caring%20about%20convention.%20I've%20run-commuted%20in%20sandals%2C%20rain%20boots%2C%20and%20strappy%20three-inch%20wedges%20(%26quot%3BAny%20shoe%20is%20a%20running%20shoe%20if%20you%20run%20in%20it!%26quot%3B%20I%20like%20to%20joke).%20I%20once%20jogged%20to%20a%204th%20of%20July%20party%20wearing%20a%20linen%20dress%2C%20balancing%20a%20tray%20of%20cookies%20in%20my%20hands%20so%20they%20wouldn't%20get%20jostled%20in%20my%20backpack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277b5a15e-6e08-4f31-b170-9945bbfe3eb9%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20faster%20and%20more%20confident%20in%20my%2030s%20than%20I%20was%20as%20a%20teen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEight%20months%20after%20moving%20to%20Seattle%2C%20I%20was%20a%20regular%20at%20local%20run%20clubs%20and%20decided%20to%20train%20for%20my%20first%20half%20marathon.%20Run-commuting%20helped%20me%20increase%20my%20weekly%20mileage%20with%20little%20effort%20since%20my%20runs%20were%20baked%20into%20trips%20I%20had%20to%20make%20anyway.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20November%2C%20I%20completed%20the%20Seattle%20Half%20Marathon%20in%20a%20time%20faster%20than%20anyone%20expected%20and%20placed%20in%20the%20top%2010%20of%20my%20age%20group.%20Since%20then%2C%20I've%20continued%20to%20break%20personal%20records%20in%20my%2030s%20that%20I%20set%2015%20years%20ago%20as%20a%20teen%20cross-country%20and%20track%20runner.%20I've%20run%20multiple%20sub-6%20miles%20and%20a%20sub-20%205k%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I'm%20only%20getting%20started.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a6de6bf6-e658-4dfd-8fe8-10ac1b973a6b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERun-commuting%20brought%20me%20connection%20and%20community%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%20miles%2C%20run-commuting%20has%20gifted%20me%20with%20connections%20I%20never%20would've%20made%2C%20conversations%20I%20never%20would've%20had.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%2C%20at%20a%20crosswalk%2C%20an%20older%20pedestrian%20glanced%20at%20my%20backpack%2C%20running%20shoes%2C%20and%20sweat-laced%20face%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20you're%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Erunning%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20it's%20faster%20than%20walking%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20replied.%20He%20smiled%20as%20he%20reminisced%20about%20his%20days%20as%20a%20400-meter%20runner%20on%20his%20high%20school%20track%20team.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20time%2C%20I%20ran%20to%20my%20co-working%20space%2C%20passing%20another%20member%20stuck%20in%20bumper-to-bumper%20traffic%20in%20his%20car.%20I%20was%20already%20opening%20my%20mail%20in%20the%20office%20by%20the%20time%20he'd%20parked%2C%20walked%20in%2C%20and%20stared%20at%20me%20incredulously.%20It%20was%20a%20great%20conversation%20starter%2C%20and%20the%20only%20time%20I%20had%20chatted%20up%20anyone%20at%20my%20co-working%20space.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThrough%20interactions%20like%20these%2C%20being%20seen%20became%20a%20good%20thing.%20I%20felt%20welcome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6a4676f-f8ad-4662-9ab5-8a52a63c5be2%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20sold%20my%20car%20and%20kept%20my%20run-commute%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20Prius%20never%20made%20it%20to%20Seattle.%20As%20weeks%20turned%20into%20months%20and%20run-commuting%20became%20a%20regular%20part%20of%20my%20life%2C%20I%20no%20longer%20needed%20my%20car.%20In%20November%202022%2C%20I%20sold%20it%20remotely%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20friend%20in%20Florida.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOriginally%2C%20run-commuting%20was%20just%20a%20way%20to%20get%20around.%20Now%2C%20it's%20a%20connection%20to%20my%20community%20and%20a%20constant%20reassurance%20that%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20comes%20my%20way%2C%20I%20have%20everything%20I%20need%20within%20me%20%E2%80%94%20or%20my%20backpack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-florida-to-seattle-started-running-for-commute-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726479482000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e33733bf0250c21492e6ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-florida-to-seattle-started-running-for-commute-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20sold%20my%20car%20