nts%20of%20the%20capital%20began%20to%20experience%20a%20lack%20of%20governance%2C%20particularly%20during%20the%20recent%20monsoon%20deluge%20when%20civic%20issues%20mounted.%20As%20the%20AAP%20controls%20the%20municipality%2C%20it%20could%20no%20longer%20attribute%20the%20city's%20woes%20solely%20to%20the%20BJP.%20The%20only%20exception%20was%20the%20NDMC%20area%2C%20which%20is%20under%20BJP%20control.%20Citizens%20expect%20timely%20redress%20and%20quality%20service%20in%20a%20city%20that%20prides%20itself%20on%20being%20the%20nation's%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECircumstances%20likely%20forced%20Kejriwal's%20hand.%20In%20his%20announcement%20to%20step%20down%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20the%20AAP%20convenor%20vowed%20to%20fight%20to%20prove%20his%20innocence%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bpeople's%20court%26quot%3B%2C%20likening%20it%20to%20an%20'%3Cem%3EAgnipariksha'%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(trial%20by%20fire).%20He%20has%20effectively%20thrown%20the%20decision%20back%20to%20the%20electorate%20of%20Delhi%2C%20who%20have%20supported%20him%20and%20his%20party%20for%20the%20past%2011%20years.%20Will%20this%20strategy%20work%20this%20time%20too%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20restrictions%20on%20Kejriwal%20mean%20he%20cannot%20attend%20his%20office%20or%20sign%20files%20in%20his%20official%20capacity%2C%20rendering%20him%20a%20lame-duck%20Chief%20Minister.%20This%20uncertainty%20and%20lack%20of%20governance%20structure%20could%20prompt%20the%20Centre%20to%20intervene.%20The%20AAP%20has%20already%20had%20multiple%20run-ins%20with%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20and%20Kejriwal%20has%20claimed%20that%20numerous%20amendments%20by%20the%20Centre%20have%20restricted%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20AAP%20government.%20His%20resignation%20will%20likely%20prevent%20the%20city%20from%20coming%20under%20President's%20Rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKejriwal%20Is%20Placing%20A%20Big%20Bet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20the%20electorate's%20track%20record%20in%20judging%20the%20political%20future%20can%20be%20unpredictable.%20While%20Vishwanath%20Pratap%20Singh's%20anti-corruption%20campaign%20around%20the%20Bofors%20deal%20led%20to%20the%20ousting%20of%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20similar%20anti-corruption%20narratives%20have%20not%20always%20translated%20into%20electoral%20victories%20elsewhere.%20Kejriwal%20is%20now%20putting%20his%20reputation%20on%20the%20line%2C%20seeking%20endorsement%20from%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirdly%2C%20Kejriwal's%20move%20could%20be%20part%20of%20a%20strategic%20calculation%20to%20re-establish%20the%20AAP's%20dominance%20in%20Delhi%2C%20which%20is%20central%20to%20its%20political%20identity.%20Delhi%20was%20where%20his%20anti-corruption%20movement%20began%20and%20subsequently%20led%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20AAP.%20After%20realising%20its%20limitations%20in%202014%2C%20the%20party%20saw%20significant%20success%20in%20Punjab%20in%202014%20and%20again%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Kejriwal's%20announcement%20has%20taken%20the%20opposition%20by%20surprise.%20The%20BJP%2C%20the%20main%20contender%2C%20lacks%20a%20clear%20face%20to%20challenge%20Kejriwal%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%2C%20now%20a%20minor%20player%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20might%20put%20forward%20one%20of%20its%20senior%20local%20leaders%20as%20an%20alternative.%20The%20political%20course%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%20will%20determine%20the%20path%20forward%2C%20including%20whether%20early%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20in%20November%2C%20as%20suggested%20by%20Kejriwal%2C%20or%20in%20February%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20will%20be%20the%20next%20Chief%20Minister%3F%26quot%3B%20This%20is%20the%20most%20anticipated%20question.%20Possible%20replacements%20include%20party%20colleagues%20such%20as%20Ministers%20Gopal%20Rai%2C%20Atishi%2C%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%2C%20or%20Speaker%20Ram%20Niwas%20Goel.%20There%20is%20also%20speculation%20th