idelines%20for%20other%20districts'%20educational%20institutions%20focus%20on%20ensuring%20safety%20and%20preventing%20virus%20spread.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Education%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UPI%20Transaction%20Limit%20Increased%20To%20Rs%205%20Lakh%20For%20These%20Payments%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%20has%20increased%20the%20limit%20for%20Unified%20Payments%20Interface%20(UPI)%20transactions%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20for%20certain%20types%20of%20payments.%20This%20change%2C%20effective%20from%20September%2016%2C%20is%20set%20to%20bring%20greater%20flexibility%20and%20convenience%20to%20users%20who%20make%20high-value%20transactions%20through%20UPI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20standard%20UPI%20transaction%20limit%20has%20been%20Rs%201%20lakh%20per%20transaction%2C%20with%20a%20slightly%20higher%20limit%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20specific%20categories%20such%20as%20capital%20markets%2C%20collections%2C%20insurance%20and%20foreign%20inward%20remittances.%20The%20new%20measure%2C%20as%20outlined%20in%20an%20NPCI%20circular%20dated%20August%2024%2C%20will%20see%20this%20limit%20increase%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20for%20transactions%20related%20to%20tax%20payments%2C%20payments%20to%20hospitals%20and%20educational%20institutions%20and%20investments%20in%20IPOs%20and%20RBI%20retail%20direct%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NPCI%20circular%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20enable%20this%20enhancement%26quot%3B%20the%20following%20conditions%20must%20be%20met%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanks%2C%20payment%20service%20providers%20(PSPs)%20and%20UPI%20apps%20must%20update%20the%20per-transaction%20limit%20for%20categories%20of%20verified%20merchants%20as%20specified%20in%20the%20annexure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcquiring%20entities%20are%20required%20to%20ensure%20that%20merchants%20classified%20under%20'MCC-9311'%20are%20exclusively%20handling%20tax%20payments.%20They%20must%20add%20these%20entities%20to%20the%20'Verified%20Merchant'%20list%20only%20after%20thorough%20due%20diligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerchants%20must%20enable%20UPI%20as%20a%20payment%20option%20for%20transactions%20up%20to%20the%20new%20limit%20specifically%20for%20tax%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NPCI's%20decision%20to%20increase%20the%20UPI%20transaction%20limit%20stems%20from%20the%20growing%20popularity%20of%20the%20payment%20method%20in%20India.%20%26quot%3BWith%20UPI%20emerging%20as%20a%20preferred%20payment%20method%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20enhance%20the%20per%20transaction%20limit%20in%20UPI%20for%20specific%20categories%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NPCI%20stated%20in%20its%20circular.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20has%20urged%20all%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20payments%20ecosystem%2C%20including%20banks%2C%20payment%20service%20providers%20and%20UPI%20apps%20to%20ensure%20their%20systems%20are%20updated%20to%20accommodate%20the%20new%20transaction%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20enhancement%20is%20expected%20to%20streamline%20high-value%20transactions%20and%20provide%20more%20options%20for%20users%20engaging%20in%20substantial%20financial%20activities.%20To%20ensure%20smooth%20transactions%20under%20the%20new%20limit%2C%20users%20are%20advised%20to%20verify%20with%20their%20banks%20and%20UPI%20service%20providers%20whether%20the%20increased%20limit%20applies%20to%20their%20specific%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726478820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ffaj9ieg8_upi-payments-generic_625x300_31_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fupi-transaction-limit-increased-to-rs-5-lakh-for-these-payments-6577136%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%20has%20increased%20the%20limit%20for%20Unified%20Payments%20Interface%20(UPI)%20tran