ss%20to%20nurture%20and%20blossom%20democratic%20values%20and%20further%20Constitutional%20ideals.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnLet%20these%20sacred%20platforms%20not%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FlBUMlVfWFK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FlBUMlVfWFK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Vice-President%20of%20India%20(%40VPIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVPIndia%2Fstatus%2F1835261086905364607%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2015%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20need%20to%20work%20in%20tandem%20and%20togetherness%20to%20nurture%20and%20blossom%20democratic%20values%20and%20further%20constitutional%20ideals.%20An%20Institution%20is%20well%20served%20when%20it%20is%20conscious%20of%20certain%20limitations.%20Some%20limitations%20are%20obvious%2C%20some%20limitations%20are%20very%20fine%2C%20they%20are%20subtle.%20Let%20these%20sacred%20platforms%20-%20judiciary%2C%20legislature%20and%20executive%20--%20not%20be%20trigger%20points%20of%20political%20inflammatory%20debate%20or%20narrative%20that%20is%20detrimental%20to%20the%20established%20institutions%20that%20serve%20the%20nation%20well%20in%20a%20challenging%20and%20daunting%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Vice%20President%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Institutions%2C%20all%20kinds%20of%20Institutions%20--%20Elections%20Commission%2C%20the%20investigative%20agencies%20they%20perform%20duty%20under%20tight%20situations%2C%20an%20observation%20can%20despirit%20them.%20It%20can%20set%20a%20political%20debate%20afloat.%20It%20can%20trigger%20a%20narrative.%20We%20have%20to%20be%20extremely%20conscious%20about%20our%20Institutions.%20They%20are%20robust%2C%20they%20are%20working%20independently%2C%20they%20are%20under%20checks%20and%20balances.%20They%20work%20under%20rule%20of%20law.%20In%20that%20situation%2C%20if%20we%20work%20in%20a%20manner%20to%20just%20generate%20some%20sensation%2C%20to%20become%20a%20focal%20point%20or%20epicenter%20of%20a%20political%20debate%20or%20a%20narrative%20that%20I%20will%20appeal%20to%20the%20concerned%20is%20wholly%20avoidable%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said%20in%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20made%20the%20strong%20remarks%20in%20his%20judgment%20on%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20petition%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20CBI%20in%20a%20case%20linked%20to%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy.%20The%20court%20granted%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20bail%2C%20six%20months%20after%20his%20arrest.%20While%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant%20did%20not%20find%20the%20arrest%20illegal%2C%20Justice%20Bhuyan%20wrote%20in%20a%20separate%20judgment%20that%20the%20CBI%20is%20a%20premier%20investigating%20agency%20and%20must%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20above%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20functional%20democracy%20governed%20by%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20perception%20matters.%20Like%20Caesar's%20wife%2C%20an%20investigating%20agency%20must%20be%20above%20board.%20Not%20long%20ago%2C%20this%20court%20has%20castigated%20the%20CBI%20comparing%20it%20to%20a%20caged%20parrot.%20It%20is%20imperative%20that%20CBI%20dispels%20the%20notion%20of%20it%20being%20a%20caged%20parrot.%20Rather%2C%20the%20perception%20should%20be%20that%20of%20an%20uncaged%20parrot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge's%20remarks%20prompted%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20to%20launch%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20and%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Union%20home%20minister%20should%20resign%20as%20this%20raises%20questions%20on%20him.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20called%20the%20CBI%20(Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation)%20a%20caged%20parrot%2C%26quot%3B%20Delhi%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20told%20the%20media%20after%20the%20top%20court's%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17264781