form%20at%20their%20level.%20Beyond%20imposters%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethey%20just%20sucked%20at%20their%20job%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelf-doubt%20can%20be%20crippling.%20Are%20you%20not%20very%20good%20at%20your%20job%20or%20is%20it%20just%20the%20imposter%20syndrome%20talking%3F%20How%20can%20you%20tell%20if%20your%20self-doubt%20%E2%80%94%20often%20that%20debilitating%20imposter%20syndrome%20%E2%80%94%20is%20justified%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20my%20over%2040%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20business%20world%2C%20I%20advise%20employees%20to%20look%20at%20three%20areas%20for%20the%20answer%3A%20what%20their%20boss%20tells%20them%2C%20what%20meetings%20they're%20invited%20to%2C%20and%20the%20results%20of%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20to%20inspect%20those%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed99901e-9c51-4dda-951e-7a1c5588a521%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EExamine%20what%20your%20boss%20and%20colleagues%20are%20telling%20you%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20direct%20way%20to%20gauge%20whether%20you're%20good%20at%20your%20work%20is%20to%20look%20at%20what%20others%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-managers-make-during-performance-reviews-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyour%20performance%20reviews%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20carefully.%20Check%20for%20objective%20statements%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20your%20work%2C%20the%20way%20you%20get%20results%2C%20and%20how%20you%20work%20with%20others.%20Be%20sure%20to%20read%20between%20the%20lines%20to%20look%20for%20half-complements%20or%20insincerity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReviews%20are%20formal%20feedback%20and%20are%20sometimes%20carefully%20crafted%20to%20give%20a%20specific%20tone.%20Check%20to%20see%20if%20the%20written%20feedback%20matches%20the%20oral%20feedback%20you%20get%20from%20your%20manager%20in%20more%20frequent%20and%20less%20formal%20settings.%20If%20you're%20getting%20good%20reviews%2C%20that%20almost%20always%20means%20you're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpwc-hr-performance-signs-good-at-job-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoing%20good%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERereading%20your%20reviews%20can%20bolster%20your%20self-esteem%20and%20combat%20looming%20imposter%20syndrome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20reviews%2C%20do%20you%20get%20unsolicited%20comments%20about%20your%20work%3F%20Whether%20good%20or%20bad%2C%20comments%20that%20come%20without%20prompting%20from%20people%20you%20trust%20are%20usually%20genuine.%20Most%20allies%20would%20stay%20silent%20rather%20than%20speak%20untruths.%20If%20you're%20hearing%20good%20words%20spoken%20to%20your%20face%2C%20you're%20probably%20good%20at%20what%20you%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20voice%20in%20the%20back%20of%20your%20head%20is%20screaming%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20they're%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdouble-edged-sword-high-performers-face-at-work-feedback-managers-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaying%20that%20to%20be%20nice%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20to%20cover%20up%20a%20real%20problem%3F%26quot%3B%20it's%20time%20to%20look%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224823c0dd-5b1d-4979-b1bd-ec0ebdb7df72%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELook%20around%20the%20room%20during%20meetings%20and%20rank%20yourself%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20places%20where%20imposter%20syndrome%20hits%20is%20during%20meetings.%20You%20look%20around%20and%20wonder%20if%20you%20deserve%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20table%2C%20and%20then%20you%20get%20the%20nagging%20feeling%20of%20%26quot%3BDo%20I%20even%20belong%20in%20this%20room%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20this%20question%20because%20it%20offers%20a%20great%20way%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-executive-combats-manages-imposter-syndrome-2023-10%5C%22%20tar