ineering%2C%20takes%20us%20inside%20the%20project.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-top-technology-projects-goldman-blackstone-morgan-stanley-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Epart%20of%20a%20series%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20highlighting%20top%20technology%20projects%20on%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20largest%20publicly%20listed%20hedge%20fund%20is%20in%20a%20multiyear%20rebuild%20of%20a%20key%20piece%20of%20technology%20that%20will%20be%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20its%20systematic%20investing%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20platform%2C%20called%20Condor%2C%20was%20initially%20designed%20to%20replace%20a%20cobbled-together%20patchwork%20of%20different%20systems%20%E2%80%94%20some%20built%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20underpinning%20Man%20AHL%2C%20the%20firm's%20systematic-trading%20arm.%20But%20Barry%20Fitzgerald%2C%20the%20lead%20technologist%20on%20the%20project%2C%20has%20bigger%20plans%3A%20more%20asset%20classes%2C%20more%20investing%20styles%2C%20and%20more%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20worst%20thing%20you%20could%20do%20with%20this%20is%20build%20something%20that%20fulfills%20our%20need%20for%20exactly%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Fitzgerald%2C%20cohead%20of%20front-office%20engineering%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20how%20we%20will%20trade%20in%20two%20years'%20time%2C%20but%20I%20would%20hope%20this%20platform%20runs%20for%2010%20years%20or%20longer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20big%20multiyear%20project%2C%20so%20it%20should%20get%20the%20payback.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMan%20anticipates%20spending%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20overall%20on%20building%20Condor.%20The%20project%20will%20involve%20almost%20everyone%20at%20Man%20AHL%20as%20well%20as%20significant%20numbers%20of%20people%20from%