%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113387553.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVivek's%20father%20provided%20him%20with%20a%20selection%20of%20perfumes%20to%20sell%2C%20and%20he%20was%20responsible%20for%20tracking%20inventory%20and%20sales.%20He%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20went%20door%20to%20door%20on%20my%20bicycle%2C%20carrying%20my%20school%20bag%20filled%20with%20the%20inventory%20and%20merchandise.%E2%80%9D%20This%20hands-on%20experience%20allowed%20him%20to%20grasp%20essential%20business%20concepts%20such%20as%20accounting%20and%20sales%20at%20a%20young%20age.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvivek-oberoi-reveals-how-selling-perfumes-at-the-age-of-10-shaped-his-entrepreneurial-journey%2Farticleshow%2F113387553.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BReaching%20Out%20For%20Fifth%2C%20Final%20Time%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Invites%20Doctors%20For%20Meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20has%20extended%20its%20fifth%20invitation%20for%20talks%20to%20junior%20doctors%20protesting%20over%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20medico%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%20The%20junior%20doctors%20have%20refused%20to%20rejoin%20work%20till%20justice%20is%20served%20in%20the%20heinous%20case%20and%20several%20top%20officials%20are%20shunted%20out.%20Earlier%20meetings%20between%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20doctors%20were%20called%20off%20due%20to%20disagreements%20on%20several%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20live-streaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20to%20the%20protesting%20doctors%2C%20Chief%20Secretary%20Manoj%20Pant%20said%20that%20the%20doctors%20must%20resume%20their%20duties%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20September%209%20directive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20fifth%20and%20final%20time%20we%20are%20reaching%20out%20to%20you%20for%20a%20meeting%20between%20the%20Honourable%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20your%20delegates.%20In%20line%20with%20our%20discussion%20from%20the%20day%20before%2C%20we%20are%20once%20again%20inviting%20you%20to%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20Honourable%20Chief%20Minister%20at%20her%20Kalighat%20residence%20for%20a%20discussion%20with%20an%20open%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20secretary%20underlined%20that%20the%20meeting%20cannot%20be%20videographed%20or%20live-streamed%20--%20the%20point%20on%20which%20the%20earlier%20meeting%20fell%20through%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20trust%20that%20good%20sense%20will%20prevail%2C%20and%20as%20mutually%20agreed%20and%20as%20per%20your%20statement%20to%20the%20media%20day%20before%20-%20there%20will%20be%20no%20live%20streaming%20or%20videography%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20given%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20sub%20judice%20in%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20the%20country.%20Instead%2C%20the%20minutes%20of%20the%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Emeeting%20will%20be%20recorded%20and%20signed%20by%20both%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20email%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20meeting%20is%20scheduled%20for%205%20PM%20today%20ie%2016th%20September%202024%20at%20Hon'ble%20Chief%20Minister's%20Kalighat%20residence.%20The%20same%20delegation%20which%20came%20for%20the%20last%20discussions%20is%20requested%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20venue%20at%204%3A45%20PM%20today.%20We%20look%20forward%20to%20your%20positive%20response%20and%20a%20productive%20and%20fruitful%20discussion%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20meetings%20planned%20between%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20junior%20doctors%20led%20to%20dramatic%20scenes.%20On%20September%2012%2C%20the%20doctors%20went%20to%20the%20state%20secretariat%20Nabanna%20to%20meet%20Ms%20Banerjee%2C%20but%20re