cipal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20tried%20to%20downplay%20the%2031-year-old%20doctor's%20rape-murder%20as%20an%20incident%20of%20suicide%20and%20this%20may%20have%20led%20to%20the%20destruction%20of%20evidence%2C%20probe%20agency%20CBI%20has%20told%20a%20Kolkata%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ghosh%2C%20earlier%20arrested%20in%20a%20case%20of%20financial%20irregularities%20at%20the%20state-run%20hospital%2C%20now%20faces%20a%20charge%20of%20tampering%20with%20evidence%20in%20the%20heinous%20case%20that%20has%20shocked%20the%20nation.%20Abhijit%20Mondal%2C%20officer-in-charge%20of%20Tala%20Police%20Station%2C%20has%20also%20been%20arrested%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CBI's%20remand%20note%20submitted%20in%20court%20yesterday%2C%20Dr%20Ghosh%20got%20information%20about%20the%20incident%20at%209.58%20am%20on%20August%209%2C%20but%20did%20not%20reach%20the%20hospital%20immediately%20and%20did%20not%20register%20a%20formal%20complaint%20with%20the%20police.%20The%20CBI's%20note%20says%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20theory%20of%20suicide%26quot%3B%20was%20introduced%20despite%20external%20injury%20marks%20on%20the%20victim's%20body.%20The%20doctors'%20parents%20have%20also%20said%20a%20phone%20call%20from%20the%20hospital%20told%20them%20that%20their%20daughter%20had%20died%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20said%20that%20Dr%20Ghosh%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20police%20officer%20and%20an%20advocate%20after%20the%20victim%20was%20found%20raped%20and%20murdered.%20The%20former%20principal%20did%20not%20even%20meet%20the%20victim's%20parents%20when%20they%20came%20to%20the%20hospital%20to%20find%20their%20daughter%20raped%20and%20murdered.%20Dr%20Ghosh%20failed%20to%20ensure%20the%20timely%20completion%20of%20medical%20formalities%20after%20the%20incident%20and%20asked%20subordinates%20to%20send%20the%20body%20to%20the%20morgue%20immediately%2C%20the%20CBI%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20remand%20note%20against%20the%20police%20officer%2C%20the%20CBI%20said%20that%20Mr%20Mondal%20got%20information%20after%20the%20heinous%20crime%20at%2010.03%20am%2C%20but%20reached%20the%20hospital%20an%20hour%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20General%20Diary%20Entry%2C%20CBI%20has%20said%2C%20mentioned%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bbody%20of%20PG%20trainee%20of%20R%20G%20Kar%20MCH%20was%20found%20lying%20in%20unconscious%20state%26quot%3B%20even%20after%20the%20body%20was%20examined%20and%20the%20victim%20found%20dead.%20The%20agency%20said%20the%20police%20officer%20failed%20to%20ensure%20timely%20registration%20of%20the%20FIR%20despite%20the%20heinous%20nature%20of%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%2C%20the%20CBI%20said%2C%20failed%20to%20cordon%20off%20the%20crime%20scene.%20This%20led%20to%20unauthorised%20people%20entering%20the%20crime%20scene%20and%20led%20to%20damage%20of%20vital%20evidence%2C%20it%20has%20said.%20The%20agency%20has%20also%20held%20him%20responsible%20for%20the%20delay%20in%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20death%20certificate%20and%20autopsy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20underlined%20that%20the%20police%20officer%20received%20information%20about%20the%20case%20at%2010.03%20am%2C%20but%20the%20FIR%20was%20filed%20late%20at%20night%20--%20an%20issue%20that%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20flagged%20in%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%2C%20the%20CBI%20said%2C%20hurriedly%20allowed%20the%20body's%20cremation%20despite%20the%20family%20members%20specifically%20demanding%20a%20second%20autopsy.%20The%20agency%20has%20said%20that%20the%20police%20officer%20started%20the%20investigation%20with%20an%20attempt%20to%20vitiate%20evidence%20and%20remained%20evasive%20when%20the%20CBI%20questioned%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kolkata%20court%20yesterday%20granted%20the%20CBI%20two%20days'%20custody%20of%20Dr%20Ghosh%20and%20Mr%20Mondal.%20The%20matter%20will%20be%20heard%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mondal's%20lawyer%20said%20there%20was%20no%20ground%20to%20arrest%20the%20police%20officer.%20%26quot%3BThey%20allege%20there%20was%20a%20delay.%20They%20don't%20say%20whether%20I%20am%20an%20accused%20or%20a%20witness.%20There%20is%20no%20ground%20for%20arrest%20here.%20This%20is%20at%20best%20a%20case%20of%20alleged%20dereliction%20of%20duty.%20For%20that%2C%20a%20departmental%20inquiry%20could%20have%20been%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ghosh%20and%20Mr%20Mondal%20are%20the%20CBI's%20first%20arrests%20in%20the%20rape-murder%20case.%20They%20are%20accused%20of%20being%20a%20part%20of%20an%20alleged%20cover-up%20by%20the%20hospital%20administration%20after%20the%20doctor%20was%20found%20raped%20and%20murdered.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20police%20arrested%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20who%20frequented%20the%20hospital%2C%20for%20allegedly%20raping%20and%20murdering%20the%20doctor.%20Roy's%20custody%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI%20after%20the%20central%20agency%20took%20over%20the%20probe%20after%20a%20high%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726471980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F54g9dgk8_kolkata-split_625x300_16_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-sandip-ghosh-ex-principal-tried-to-downplay-doctor-rape-murder-as-suicide-cbi-to-court-6576102%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20former%20principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20tried%20to%20downplay%20the%2031-year-old%20doctor's%20rape-murder%20as%20an%20incident%20of%20suicide%20and%20this%20may%20have%20led%20to%20the%20destruction%20of%20evidence%2C%20probe%20agency%20CBI%20has%20told%20a%20Kolkata%20court%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-