ttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113386054%2Cimgsize-54468.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwho-is-gisele-pelicot-drugged-and-raped-for-a-decade-woman-becomes-symbol-of-courage-and-resilience%2Farticleshow%2F113383469.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113383469.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20France%2C%20hundreds%20have%20shown%20support%20for%20Gis%C3%A8le%20P%C3%A9licot%2C%20who%20accused%20her%20ex-husband%20of%20drugging%20and%20facilitating%20her%20rape%20by%20strangers%20over%20ten%20years.%20The%20ongoing%20trial%20involves%2050%20men%20and%20has%20garnered%20significant%20attention%2C%20highlighting%20issues%20of%20sexual%20violence%20and%20consent.%20P%C3%A9licot's%20bravery%20has%20been%20widely%20praised.%20She%20has%20made%20her%20court%20case%20public%20so%20that%20people%20can%20be%20alerted.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwho-is-gisele-pelicot-drugged-and-raped-for-a-decade-woman-becomes-symbol-of-courage-and-resilience%2Farticleshow%2F113383469.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwho-is-gisele-pelicot-drugged-and-raped-for-a-decade-woman-becomes-symbol-of-courage-and-resilience%2Famp_articleshow%2F113383469.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwho-is-gisele-pelicot-drugged-and-raped-for-a-decade-woman-becomes-symbol-of-courage-and-resilience%2Famp_articleshow%2F113383469.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225-Year-Old%20Attacked%2C%20Injured%20By%20Pack%20Of%20Stray%20Dogs%20In%20Pune%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20five-year-old%20child%20was%20severely%20injured%20after%20being%20attacked%20by%20a%20pack%20of%20dogs%20in%20Chakan%20in%20Pune%20district%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shocking%20video%20(the%20incident%20was%20captured%20by%20a%20nearby%20CCTV%20camera)%2C%20the%20young%20boy%20can%20be%20seen%20standing%20by%20the%20side%20of%20a%20partly-flooded%20dirt%20road%20and%20waving%20away%20at%20a%20black%20dog.%20The%20boy%20does%20not%20move%20toward%20the%20dog%20and%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20make%20any%20threatening%20gesture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeconds%20later%20a%20second%20dog%20sprints%20forward%20from%20the%20boy's%20right%20hand%20side.%20The%20dog%20attacks%20the%20boy%20before%20he%20can%20run%20away.%20The%20CCTV%20feed%20captures%20the%20young%20boy's%20scream%20as%20the%20dog%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20boy%20is%20thrown%20to%20the%20ground%20at%20least%20half-a-dozen%20other%20dogs%20converge%2C%20barking%20and%20surrounding%20the%20boy%2C%20who%20continues%20screaming.%20The%20terrified%20boy%20is%20soon%20pinned%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20the%20dogs%20circle%20around%2C%20even%20seeming%20to%20jump%20on%20the%20young%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20screams%20and%20the%20dogs'%20barking%20bring%20a%20woman%20racing%20out%20of%20a%20nearby%20house.%20She%20throws%20a%20few%20stones%20at%20the%20dogs%20but%20they%20continue%20their%20attack%2C%20seeming%20to%20drag%20the%20child%20into%20nearby%20bushes.%20Then%20two%20men%20appear%20on%20the%20scene%20and%20rush%20at%20the%20dogs%2C%20who%20then%20race%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2F76-year-old-woman-dies-after-stray-dog-attack-in-bengaluru-cops-6436263%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E76-Year-Old%20Woman%20Dies%20After%20Stray%20Dog%20Attack%20In%20Bengaluru%3A%20Cops%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20disturbing%20incident%20has%20reignited%20the%20debate%20over%20attacks%20by%20stray%20dogs%20in%20Pune%2C%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20Last%20month%20there%20was%20a%20horrific%20incident%20from%20Telangana's%20Rajanna%20Sircilla%20district%20in%20which%20an%20elderly%20woman%20was%20killed%20by%20pack%20of%20stray%20dogs%20which%20then%20ate%20parts%20of%20her%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstray-dogs-kill-eat-body-parts-of-82-year-old-woman-in-telangana-police-6243140%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStray%20Dogs%20Kill%2C%20Eat%20Body%20Parts%20Of%2082-Year-Old%20Woman%20In%20Telangana%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20incidents%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20several%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Kerala%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%20have%20led%20to%20renewed%20calls%20for%20stricter%20measures%20to%20control%20stray%20dog%20populations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Dr%20Abi%20T%20Vanak%2C%20Director%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Design%20at%20the%20Ashoka%20Trust%20For%20Research%20In%20Ecology%20And%20The%20Environment%2C%20said%20the%20problem%20of%20stray%20dogs%20%26quot%3Bhas%20become%20completely%20out%20of%20control%20(and)%20a%20human%20rights%20issue%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20certainly%20blame%20unscientific%20animal%20birth%20control%20policies...%20because%20first%2C%20they%20created%20a%20category%20called%20'street%20dog'%20and%20said%20they%20can%20only%20live%20on%20the%20street%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20according%20to%20the%20rules%2C%20even%20if%20the%20Pune%20officials%20capture%20these%20dogs%2C%20they%20only%20have%20to%20observe%20them%20for%2010%20days%20and%20they%20will%20be%20released.%20But%20dogs%20kept%20in%20cages%20are%20not%20going%20to%20attack...%20they%20are%20going%20to%20be%20scared.%20So%2C%20most%20likely%2C%20the%20officials%20won't%20find%20anything%20wrong%20and%20the%20dogs%20will%20be%20released%20and%20then%20will%20probably%20be%20more%20aggressive...%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20the%20problem%20really%20is%2C%20we%20have%20created%20this%20situation%20where%20poor%20people%20continue%20to%20suffer%20the%20brunt%20of%20attacks%20like%20this%20because%20of%20poor%20policy-making%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Vanak%20told%20NDTV%2C%20suggesting%20society%20needs%20to%20%26quot%3Brethink%20the%20relationship%20with%20dogs%2C%20as%20they%20are%20domestic%20and%20not%20feral%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can%20go%20feral%20sometimes%20but%20are%20maintained%20by%20humans...%20so%20we%20have%20to%20ensure%20their%20well-being.%20And%20that%20cannot%20be%20done%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20so%20we%20have%20to%20change%20this%20policy.%20People%20should%20be%20encouraged%20to%20adopt%20dogs%20and%20set%20up%20shelters.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20feed%20them%2C%20then%20feed%20them%20at%20shelters.%20Currently%20the%20rules%20even%20require%20stray%20dogs%20to%20be%20fed%20on%20the%20streets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Vanak%20also%20pointed%20out%20India%20has%20a%20population%20of%20around%2080%20million%20dogs%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20that%20the%20current%20ABC%2C%20or%20animal%20birth%20control%2C%20laws%20are%20%26quot%3Bimpractical%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20effectively%20control%20population%20of%20free-ranging%20dogs%20(under%20current%20rules%2C%20which%20focus%20only%20on%20urban%20areas)%2C%20you%20have%20to%20sterilise%20something%20like%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20numbers.%20And%20this%20has%20to%20be%20done%20indefinitely%20because%2C%20if%20you%20stop%2C%20non-sterlised%20dogs%20from%20other%20areas%20will%20come%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPune%20district%20authorities%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20urged%20parents%20to%20remain%20vigilant%20and%20supervise%20children%20while%20outdoors%2C%20particularly%20in%20remote%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726470300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fkq2bia5o_pune-dog-attack-_625x300_16_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-stray-dogs-attack-child-5-year-old-attacked-injured-by-pack-of-stray-dogs-in-pune-6576182%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20five-year-old%20child%20was%20severely%20injured%20after%20being%20attacked%20by%20a%20pack%20of%20dogs%20in%20Chakan%20in%20Pune%20district%20in%20Maharashtra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-stray-dogs-attack-child-5-year-old-attacked-injured-by-pack-of-stray-dogs-in-pune-6576182%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Yemen's%20Houthi%20Rebels%20Got%20Hold%20Of%20Ballistic%20Missiles%20To%20Attack%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYemen's%20Houthi%20rebels%20launched%20a%20ballistic%20missile%20that%20struck%20near%20Israel's%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20a%20bustling%20commercial%20hub%20on%20Sunday.%20Rebel%20Houthi%20leader%20Abdul%20Malik%20al-Houthi%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20missile%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bballistic%20missile%26quot%3B%20that%20penetrated%20Israel's%20sophisticated%20air%20defence%20systems.%20While%20there%20were%20no%20casualties%2C%20the%20attack%20added%20to%20the%20already%20fragile%20regional%20tensions%2C%20particularly%20as%20the%20Gaza%20war%2C%20triggered%20by%20Hamas'%20attack%20on%20October%207%2C%20neared%20its%20first%20anniversary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20was%20quick%20to%20respond%2C%20warning%20that%20the%20Iran-backed%20Houthi%20rebels%20would%20%26quot%3Bpay%20a%20heavy%20price%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20strike.%20While%20the%20missile%20caused%20only%20minor%20damage%20-%20shattering%20glass%20at%20a%20train%20station%20and%20injuring%20several%20civilians%20on%20their%20way%20to%20shelters%20-%20the%20symbolic%20nature%20of%20the%20attack%20cannot%20be%20understated.%20It%20is%20the%20latest%20escalation%20involving%20the%20Houthis%2C%20who%20have%20increasingly%20been%20drawn%20into%20the%20Gaza%20conflict%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20network%20of%20militias%20collectively%20known%20as%20Iran's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-palestine-gaza-explained-axis-of-resistance-and-irans-proxy-network-across-middle-east-4534061%5C%22%3EAxis%20of%20Resistance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20prompted%20questions%20about%20how%20a%20militia%20in%20war-torn%20Yemen%20has%20managed%20to%20acquire%20the%20capability%20to%20launch%20such%20long-range%20missile%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrigins%20Of%20The%20Houthis'%20Missile%20Capabilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis'%20ability%20to%20acquire%20and%20launch%20ballistic%20missiles%20lies%20in%20historical%20weapons%20caches%2C%20Iranian%20support%2C%20and%20arms%20trafficking.%20The%20group%2C%20officially%20known%20as%20Ansar%20Allah%2C%20evolved%20from%20a%20grassroots%20religious%20movement%20in%20the%201990s%20to%20a%20powerful%20militia%20with%20sophisticated%20weapons.%20Since%20the%20Yemeni%20civil%20war%20broke%20out%20in%202015%2C%20the%20Houthis%20have%20relied%20on%20three%20primary%20sources%20to%20build%20their%20missile%20arsenal%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EYemeni%20Government%20Missiles%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20Yemen%20was%20divided%20into%20North%20and%20South%2C%20with%20each%20side%20receiving%20military%20aid%20from%20competing%20superpowers.%20The%20Yemeni%20government%20fir