n%20a%20podcast%2C%20the%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20judge%20reflected%20on%20her%20upbringing%20in%20a%20middle-class%20family%20and%20how%20she%20once%20felt%20insecure%20about%20not%20owning%20designer%20items.%20Now%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20youngest%20CEOs%20in%20India%2C%20she%20no%20longer%20feels%20the%20need%20to%20prove%20her%20worth%20through%20luxury%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20bring%20myself%20to%20buy%20a%20luxury%20car.%20I%20can%20afford%20it%2C%20but%20I%20just%20can't%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gupta%20shared.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20I%20think%20about%20buying%20one%20with%20a%20bonus%2C%20I%20remind%20myself%20that%20a%20car%20is%20a%20depreciating%20asset.%20I%20don't%20even%20drive%2C%20and%20the%20moment%20I%20take%20it%20out%2C%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20value%20is%20gone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20recalled%20how%2C%2018%20years%20ago%2C%20fresh%20out%20of%20college%2C%20she%20would%20feel%20insecure%20when%20people%20pointed%20out%20her%20lack%20of%20expensive%20items.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20if%20someone%20asks%20why%20I%20drive%20an%20Innova%2C%20I%20can%20confidently%20say%2C%20'My%20life%2C%20my%20choice.'%20I%20no%20longer%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20prove%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Ms%20Gupta%20took%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20to%20express%20her%20thoughts%20on%20how%20today's%20young%20people%20are%20funding%20luxurious%20lifestyles%20by%20making%20risky%20investments.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20seen%20people%20in%20their%2020s%20saying%20they%20don't%20need%20to%20work%20because%20they%20are%20busy%20doing%20F%26amp%3BO.%20Young%20women%20who%20say%20their%20lifestyle%20and%20handbags%20are%20funded%20by%20trading%20gains%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20post%2C%20Ms%20Gupta%20also%20shared%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Economic%20Survey%202023-24%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Economic%20Survey%20highlights%20this%20in%20some%20very%20strong%20language.%20Other%20regulators%20have%20also%20rightly%20and%20repeatedly%20warned%20us%20about%20this.%26quot%3B%20She%20claimed%20that%20since%20this%20type%20of%20liquidity%20is%20hazardous%20for%20individuals%20as%20well%20as%20the%20economy%2C%20it%20is%20finally%20time%20for%20action%20to%20be%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726469640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2Fvec8l1ok_radhika-gupta_625x300_06_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fi-can-afford-but-edelweiss-radhika-gupta-on-why-she-doesnt-own-luxury-cars-6576165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20judge%20reflected%20on%20her%20upbringing%20in%20a%20middle-class%20family%20and%20how%20she%20once%20felt%20insecure%20about%20not%20owning%20designer%20items.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fi-can-afford-but-edelweiss-radhika-gupta-on-why-she-doesnt-own-luxury-cars-6576165%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akshay%20to%20work%20with%20National%20award-winning%20director%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726468847000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113385011%2Cimgsize-34628.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fakshay-kumar-teams-up-with-national-award-winning-director-sanjay-puran-singh-chauhan-for-tirangaa-report%2Farticleshow%2F113385058.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113385058.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EChauhan%2C%20who%20has%20previously%20directed%20critically%20acclaimed%20films%20such%20as%20Lahore%20(2010)%20and%2072%20Hoorain%20(2023)%2C%20both%20of%20which%20received%20National%20Awards%2C%2