presents%20an%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%2015%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Urbanisation%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20built-up%20area%20increased%20by%2020%25%20from%201969%20to%202017.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20built-up%20area%20around%20major%20towns%20increased%20by%20about%2075%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Glacier%20shrinkage%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGlaciers%20in%20the%20region%20have%20shrunk%20by%2040%25%20in%20area%20and%2025%25%20in%20volume%20since%20around%201650%20AD.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20reduces%20the%20glacier%20melt%20that%20replenishes%20groundwater.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20study%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20specific%20measurements%20of%20groundwater%20level%20decline%2C%20it%20states%20that%20these%20factors%20have%20led%20to%20an%20imbalance%20between%20water%20demand%20and%20supply%2C%20decline%20of%20shallow%20resources%2C%20reduction%20of%20natural%20discharge%2C%20drying%20of%20springs%2C%20and%20decline%20in%20water%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWithout%20immediate%20intervention%2C%20the%20quality%20and%20quantity%20of%20Leh%E2%80%99s%20groundwater%20will%20continue%20to%20decline%20rapidly%20over%20the%20next%2020%E2%80%9330%20years.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20countdown%20we%20cannot%20ignore%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Chorol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolutions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20actionable%20solutions%20that%20the%20local%20government%2C%20administration%2C%20business%20owners%2C%20and%20residents%20can%20take%20to%20address%20the%20growing%20concern%20surrounding%20groundwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Stricter%20regulations%20for%20groundwater%20extraction%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mandatory%20permits%20for%20groundwater%20