2%3A%22Food%20Startup%20%E2%80%98Tocco%E2%80%99%20Helps%20People%20in%20Their%2050s%20Build%20an%20Identity%20Through%20Cooking%2C%20Earns%20Rs%201%20Cr%2FYr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20paid%20for%20my%20own%20trip%20and%20went%20to%20Dubai!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20platform%20helped%20me%20build%20my%20identity.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20very%20confident%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20menopause%2C%20staying%20busy%20is%20crucial%20to%20keep%20mood%20swings%20at%20bay.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20chefs%20of%20Tocco%2C%20an%20e-commerce%20platform%20that%20curates%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359581%2Finspiring-senior-citizens-india-running-successful-startups-isro-restaurants-oil-business-daycares%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome-cooked%20specialties%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20across%20the%20country.%20From%20Uma%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20prawn%20pickles%20in%20Kerala%20to%20Bhavana%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Enankhatais%20%3C%2Fem%3E(biscuits)%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Annie%20Philip%E2%80%99s%20matured%20plum%20cake%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Tocco%20is%20a%20melting%20pot%20of%20regional%20delicacies!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20women%20can%20be%20found%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20you%20just%20need%20to%20look%20and%20spend%20a%20few%20minutes%20talking%20to%20them.%20Ask%20your%20mother%20or%20aunt%20about%20their%20wishes%2C%20and%20if%20they%20are%20anything%20like%20Bhavana%20or%20Uma%2C%20they%20would%20have%20definitely%20harboured%20dreams%20of%20creating%20their%20own%20identity%20through%20cooking.%20Tocco%20makes%20it%20easy%20for%20neighbourhood%20home%20chefs%20to%20do%20just%20that%2C%20without%20the%20hassle%20of%20branding%20or%20marketing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20for%20this%20platform%20was%20born%20from%20founder%20Reshma%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20own%20desire%20to%20experience%20the%20taste%20of%20home%20while%20living%20away.%20After%20moving%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20work%2C%20she%20found%20herself%20caught%20in%20the%20cycle%20of%20eating%20outside%2C%20always%20craving%20her%20%3Cem%3Eamma%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20tasty%20food.%20Realising%20she%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20one%20looking%20for%20authentic%20Kerala%20food%2C%20she%20started%20making%20banana%20chips%20and%20selling%20them%20through%20her%20brand%2C%20%E2%80%98MeenGurry%20Memories%E2%80%99%2C%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPacking%20memories%20of%20her%20%3Cem%3Eamma%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Eammamma%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmother%E2%80%99s)%20generations-old%20recipe%20for%20the%20perfect%2C%20thin%2C%20and%20crispy%20banana%20chips%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20game-changer%20for%20Reshma%2C%20who%20was%20then%20working%20at%20an%20AI%2Fhealthcare%20startup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tocco%20chef%20Annie%20baking%20a%20plum%20cake.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828-150x200.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.06.57-1726037828.jpeg%20960w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365472%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETocco%20chef%20Annie%20baking%20a%20plum%20cake.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20passion%20project%20soon%20took%20on%20a%20life%20of%20its%20own%20when%20she%20introduced%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20prawn%20and%20mango%20pickle.%20Rather%20than%20making%20the%20food%20herself%2C%20Reshma%20decided%20to%20create%20a%20platform%20where%20people%20like%20her%20mother%20and%20aunt%20could%20sell%20their%20dishes%20directly.%20This%20would%20help%20them%20become%20financially%20independent%20and%20turn%20their%20passion%20into%20a%20thriving%20business.%20For%20customers%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20way%20to%20enjoy%20the%20local%20delicacies%20they%20crave!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%202023%2C%20Tocco%20now%20has%20over%2016%20chefs%2C%20both%20men%20and%20women%2C%20mostly%20in%20their%2050s%2C%20whose%20dreams%20have%20been%20given%20wings%20through%20the%20platform!%20Starting%20with%20just%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355942%2Forganic-masala-spices-in-coimbatore-tamil-nadu-iniya-organics-business-podis-health-mixes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebootstrapped%20business%20%3C%2Fa%3Eachieved%20a%20turnover%20of%20over%20Rs%201%20crore%20in%20the%20current%20year.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20Reshma%20is%20empowering%20those%20with%20a%20lifelong%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPacking%20childhood%20memories%20in%20a%20box%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReshma%2C%20an%20engineer%2C%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20in%202012%20for%20work.%20She%20worked%20in%20healthcare%20startups%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20gaining%20first-hand%20experience%20in%20healthcare%20and%20health%20tech.%20Joining%20these%20startups%20from%20their%20infancy%2C%20she%20had%20a%20front-row%20understanding%20of%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20scale%20a%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusy%20with%20work%2C%20a%20huge%20portion%20of%20her%2020s%20was%20spent%20eating%20out%20or%20cooking%20for%20herself.%20She%20constantly%20craved%20a%20good%20home-cooked%20meal%2C%20just%20like%20the%20ones%20her%20mother%20used%20to%20make.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20missed%20my%20roots%20and%20the%20food%20I%20grew%20up%20eating.%20Every%20time%20I%20visited%20home%20in%20Kochi%2C%20I%20brought%20back%20staples%20like%20banana%20chips%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Epodis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spice%20powders)%2C%20which%20made%20cooking%20a%20meal%20very%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20women%20of%20Tocco%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821-300x168.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821-500x280.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821-768x431.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-women-1726037821-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365471%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22718%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20women%20of%20Tocco.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20consistent%20and%20convenient%20supply%20of%20food%20that%20reminded%20me%20of%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Reshma%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20hectic%20schedule%20coupled%20with%20late%20nights%20led%20to%20lots%20of%20restaurant%20meals.%20A%20few%20years%20later%2C%20Reshma%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20PCOS%20(Polycystic%20Ovary%20Syndrome).%20This%20diagnosis%20triggered%20her%20search%20for%20healthier%2C%20authentic%2C%20home-cooked%20regional%20food.%20Unfortunately%2C%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20anything%20like%20it%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20sister%2C%20Annu%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20faced%20the%20same%20dilemma%20%E2%80%94%20failing%20to%20find%20meals%20that%20bottled%20the%20memories%20of%20Kerala.%20Long%20discussions%20between%20the%20sisters%20led%20to%20Reshma%20creating%20experience%20boxes%20in%202021%2C%20offering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353263%2Fphilos-pickles-kerala-delivery-india-how-to-start-a-homemade-pickle-business-tips-tincy-thomas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20Kerala%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20weekends.%20Prepared%20in%20her%20Mumbai%20kitchen%2C%20one%20dish%20clearly%20stood%20out%20%E2%80%94%20the%20banana%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20she%20decided%20to%20sell%20these%20chips%20under%20her%20venture%20%E2%80%98MeenGurry%20Memories%E2%80%99%20(%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emeen%20gurry%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20means%20fish%20curry)%2C%20as%20a%20homage%20to%20their%20shared%20memories%20around%20the%20dining%20table.%20Every%20weekend%2C%20she%20curated%20different%20meal%20boxes%20while%20continuing%20her%20job%20during%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20running%20MeenGurry%20Memories%2C%20Reshma%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20do%20something%20to%20promote%20chefs%20like%20her%20mother%20Uma%20and%20aunt%20Lakshmi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reshma%20with%20her%20freshly%20made%20banana%20chips%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840-150x200.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-20.29.28-1726037840.jpeg%20960w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365474%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EReshma%20with%20her%20freshly%20made%20banana%20chips.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sister%20duo%2C%20Uma%20and%20Lakshmi%2C%20had%20participated%20in%20a%20cooking%20contest%20on%20a%20TV%20channel%20called%20%E2%80%98Mazhavil%20Manorama%E2%80%99%20in%202019.%20They%20were%20among%20the%20semi-finalists%2C%20which%20was%20a%20huge%20motivation%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20immense%20potential%20for%20people%20like%20our%20parents%20who%20are%20retired%20or%20living%20alone.%20They%20need%20to%20be%20engaged.%20I%20then%20asked%20my%20mother%20to%20make%20her%20famous%20prawn%20and%20mango%20pickle%2C%20a%20childhood%20favourite%20of%20many.%20I%20packaged%20it%20and%20started%20selling%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Reshma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20Lakshmi%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Emulga%20podi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(gun%20powder)%2C%20%3Cem%3Esambar%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%2C%20and%20other%20products%20were%20also%20introduced.%20Reshma%2C%20an%20MBA%20graduate%20from%20IIT%20Bombay%2C%20then%20created%20a%20platform%20to%20sell%20these%20nostalgic%20products%2C%20naming%20it%20%E2%80%98Tocco%E2%80%99.%20The%20name%2C%20short%20for%20%E2%80%98The%20Orange%20Candy%20Co%E2%80%99%2C%20made%20sense%20because%2C%20for%20Reshma%2C%20the%20ultimate%20symbol%20of%20nostalgia%20was%20the%20orange%20candies%20she%20shared%20with%20her%20sister%20during%20childhood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Tocco%2C%20the%20aim%20was%20to%20pack%20this%20childhood%20nostalgia%20in%20a%20box%20for%20other%20people%20to%20enjoy.%20In%20late%202022%2C%20she%20quit%20her%20job%20to%20fully%20focus%20on%20building%20the%20platform.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20onboarding%20the%20first%20two%20chefs%2C%20Reshma%20brought%20in%20more%2C%20expanding%20the%20platform%20to%20include%20over%2016%20chefs%20from%20different%20cities%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%20They%20offer%20snacks%20like%20banana%20chips%2C%20jackfruit%20chips%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshankarpali%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20sweet%20snack)%3Cem%3E%2C%20masalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20%3Cem%3Echaat%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%20sambar%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Erasam%20podi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spice%20powder)%2C%20pickles%20like%20prawn%2C%20cut%20mango%2C%20homemade%20curd%20chilli%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Epuli%20inji%20%3C%2Fem%3E(ginger%20pickle)%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2058-year-old%20Uma%20Suresh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20cooking%20since%20she%20was%20in%20Class%206%2C%20Tocco%20has%20given%20new%20meaning%20to%20her%20life.%20%E2%80%9CCooking%20is%20my%20passion.%20I%20would%20always%20pack%20some%20pickles%20for%20anyone%20who%20came%20home.%20I%20always%20dreamed%20of%20running%20a%20business%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to.%20Thanks%20to%20my%20daughters%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20made%20a%20name%20for%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Uma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC89D7o5SBhy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC89D7o5SBhy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC89D7o5SBhy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20MeenGurry%20Memories%20(%40meengurry_memories)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Uma%20and%20her%20sister%20Lakshmi%20embarked%20on%20trips%20to%20Dubai%20and%20Goa%20using%20their%20own%20earnings!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavana%20Shah%2C%2051%2C%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20who%20makes%20snacks%20and%20starters%20and%20runs%20cooking%20classes%2C%20says%20Tocco%20has%20given%20her%20a%20renewed%20sense%20of%20vigour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWork%20is%20very%20important%20for%20women%20over%2050%2C%20especially%20when%20going%20through%20menopause.%20Dealing%20with%20the%20hot%20flashes%20and%20mood%20swings%20is%20easier%20when%20we%20are%20busy.%20While%20I%20had%20regular%20customers%20in%20Vile%20Parle%2C%20Tocco%20has%20helped%20people%20across%20the%20country%20discover%20who%20I%20am.%20I%20thank%20Reshma%20for%20giving%20me%20a%20new%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhavana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20also%20offers%20flexibility%20to%20chefs%20like%20Bhavana%2C%20who%20occasionally%20travels%20abroad%20to%20visit%20her%20children.%20Additionally%2C%20Tocco%20assists%20with%20branding%20and%20marketing%2C%20which%20are%20major%20challenges%20in%20establishing%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Rs%205%2C000%20to%20Rs%201%20crore!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reshma%2C%20the%20team%20at%20Tocco%20ensures%20that%20all%20products%20are%20homemade%2C%20carefully%20crafted%20in%20small%20batches%2C%20and%20preservative-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20become%20a%20chef%20at%20Tocco%2C%20one%20must%20apply%20on%20the%20website.%20After%20an%20initial%20call%2C%20the%20top%20three%20dishes%20of%20the%20chef%20are%20discussed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20dishes%20must%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349127%2Fwoman-startup-bakery-cakelicious-cake-tubs-in-kolkata-fatema-barodawala-single-mother-business-shark-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%2C%20preservative%20free%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20a%20shelf%20life%20of%20at%20least%2030%20days.%20They%20should%20be%20regional%20or%20local%20specialities.%20We%20ask%20them%20for%20an%20ingredient%20list%20and%20take%20the%20next%20steps%20based%20on%20that.%20No%20palm%20oil%20is%20allowed.%20Chefs%20send%20samples%20of%20their%20dishes%2C%20which%20a%20focus%20group%20tastes.%20We%20suggest%20changes%2C%20and%20if%20satisfied%2C%20we%20begin%20the%20onboarding%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Reshma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tips%20to%20start%20a%20business%20from%20home%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365440%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20most%20chefs%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20brand%20of%20their%20own%2C%20Tocco%20helps%20them%20with%20the%20packaging%2C%20branding%2C%20and%20labelling.%20They%20inspect%20their%20kitchens%2C%20train%20them%2C%20and%20even%20help%20with%20getting%20an%20FSSAI%20certification%2C%20in%20case%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Tocco%20receives%20an%20order%2C%20they%20send%20it%20to%20the%20chef%2C%20who%20makes%20the%20dish%20to%20order%20and%20ships%20it.%20The%20platform%20handles%20order%20management%2C%20packing%2C%20shipping%2C%20and%20customer%20care.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20provide%20access%20to%20healthy%2C%20homemade%20food%20for%20busy%20people.%20The%20biggest%20motivation%20is%20seeing%20chefs%20like%20my%20mother%20live%20an%20independent%20life%20thanks%20to%20their%20earnings.%20Many%20of%20them%20would%20not%20have%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20sell%20their%20products%20on%20a%20large%20scale.%20We%20are%20providing%20an%20opportunity%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Tocco%20processes%20over%201%2C000%20orders%20per%20month.%20They%20plan%20to%20onboard%20more%20chefs%20and%20expand%20their%20operations.%20Reshma%20divides%20her%20time%20between%20Mumbai%20and%20Kochi%2C%20where%20she%20has%20set%20up%20a%20facility%20for%20manufacturing%20the%20banana%20chips%2C%20one%20of%20their%20best%20selling%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165-500x648.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20Bhavana%20baking%20nankhatai.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165-500x648.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165-232x300.jpeg%20232w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165-150x194.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165.jpeg%20742w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365479%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChef%20Bhavana%20baking%20%3Cem%3Enankhatai%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reshma%2C%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20is%20convincing%20customers%20to%20wait%20for%20their%20orders.%20%E2%80%9COur%20USP%20is%20that%20everything%20is%20made%20in%20small%20batches.%20With%20the%20rise%20of%20quick%20commerce%2C%20customers%20sometimes%20expect%20next-day%20delivery%2