it%E2%80%99s%20their%20distress.%20Hold%20space%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAsk%20them%20what%20they%20need%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBe%20curious%20and%20ask%20them%20questions.%20Try%20to%20understand%20what%20is%20wrong%20and%20what%E2%80%99s%20bothering%20them.%20Ask%20them%20what%20you%20can%20do%20to%20help%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAsk%20relevant%20questions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAsk%20them%20about%20their%20experiences%20and%20when%20they%20started%20feeling%20this%20way.%20Try%20to%20understand%20what%20contributed%20to%20it.%20Ask%20them%20what%20you%20could%20do%20to%20help%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Priyanka%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CSeek%20their%20permission%20before%20sharing%20suicide%20helpline%20numbers%20or%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%E2%80%99s%20number.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Mindful%20and%20compassionate%20parenting%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20witnessing%20an%20alarming%20rise%20in%20student%20suicides%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%C2%A0%20A%20report%20titled%20%3Cem%3EStudent%20Suicides%3A%20An%20Epidemic%20Sweeping%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20draws%20data%20from%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%2C%20reveals%20that%20student%20suicides%20have%20increased%20by%204%20percent%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20which%20is%20double%20the%20national%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_uYWkDoUAd%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%